chaft und Religionsphilosophie.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 4aAbwägende Venunft. 4aPhilosophiegeschichte. 4aRational consideration. 4ahistory of philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / History & Surveys / General.2bisacsh1 aBormann, Franz-Josef, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSchröer, Christian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt0 cprintz978311017517240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311089619040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110896190423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110896190.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK